<LanguageData>
    
    <!-- EN: arranged -->
    <RomanceOnTheRim_RomanceAttempt_Arranged.label>手动</RomanceOnTheRim_RomanceAttempt_Arranged.label>
    <!-- EN: All romance attempts must be under the control of the whole society.\n\n<color=#E5E54C>Effect:</color>\n - Pawns with this precept will not attempt or accept romance naturally. \n - You can control romance attempt in the right-click menu. -->
    <RomanceOnTheRim_RomanceAttempt_Arranged.description>成为恋人的前提是获得社会允许。\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C>效果:&lt;/color>\n - 拥有该戒律的殖民者不会主动或接受告白 \n - 你可以用右键菜单进行告白行为，但它们不一定成功.</RomanceOnTheRim_RomanceAttempt_Arranged.description>
    
    <!-- EN: discouraged -->
    <RomanceOnTheRim_RomanceAttempt_Discouraged.label>不提倡</RomanceOnTheRim_RomanceAttempt_Discouraged.label>
    <!-- EN: Romance on the rim is dead.\n\n<color=#E5E54C>Effect:</color>\n - (Initiator)Romance attempt chance -50% \n - (Recipient)Natural romance attempt success chance -50%. -->
    <RomanceOnTheRim_RomanceAttempt_Discouraged.description>边缘世界没有爱情。\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C>效果:&lt;/color>\n - (提出者)主动告白概率 -50% \n - (接受者)接受告白概率 -50%.</RomanceOnTheRim_RomanceAttempt_Discouraged.description>
    
    <!-- EN: encouraged -->
    <RomanceOnTheRim_RomanceAttempt_Encouraged.label>提倡</RomanceOnTheRim_RomanceAttempt_Encouraged.label>
    <!-- EN: Love is danger, love is pleasure.\nLove is pure, the only treasure.\n\n<color=#E5E54C>Effect:</color>\n - (Initiator)Romance attempt chance +50% \n - (Recipient)Natural romance attempt success chance +50%. -->
    <RomanceOnTheRim_RomanceAttempt_Encouraged.description>爱情危机四伏，爱里欢愉无数，爱是永恒的珍宝。\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C>效果:&lt;/color>\n - (提出者)主动告白概率 +50% \n - (接受者)接受告白概率 +50%.</RomanceOnTheRim_RomanceAttempt_Encouraged.description>
    
    <!-- EN: forbidden -->
    <RomanceOnTheRim_RomanceAttempt_Forbidden.label>禁止</RomanceOnTheRim_RomanceAttempt_Forbidden.label>
    <!-- EN: Everyone in our society should keep purely single.\n\n<color=#E5E54C>Effect:</color>\n - Pawns with this precept will not attempt or accept romance naturally. -->
    <RomanceOnTheRim_RomanceAttempt_Forbidden.description>社会中的每一个人都应该保持纯洁的单身。\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C>效果:&lt;/color>\n - 拥有该戒律的殖民者不会主动或接受浪漫尝试.</RomanceOnTheRim_RomanceAttempt_Forbidden.description>
    
